column5: The apartment is in the heart of Austin's most popular area. It is a 5-minute drive from downtown's best night spots (Rainey street, West 6th, Warehouse District, and 6th Street). It is located in West Campus, the neighborhood across from the UT Austin campus. Walking distance from the Capital. Any kind of being is more than welcome to stay here and would like to say that there shall be no discrimination on my behalf.
column8: Entire Apt in West Campus, right next to Downtown
